item.title: 34th Roots & Wings Annual Run/Walk 2011
item.description: Facebook status on July 24 at 12:40am 1750 to beat. Facebook status on July 24 at 9:57am 1753 seconds to finish; just 3 seconds dammit. Says it all, doesn’t it? Roots & Wings T-Shirt It was the 34th Roots & Wings Annual Run/Walk 2011 (in Milwaukee marks the beginning of the Northwestern Mutual’s Annual Meeting of the Association of Network Representatives) and there I was a good 5 minutes late at the start line!
